longBusinessSummary: NG Energy International Corp., an oil and gas company, engages in the exploration and development activities in Colombia. It holds working interest in the Maria Conchita Block, the SN-9 Block, and the Tiburon Block oil and gas properties. The company was formerly known as NGX Energy International Corp. and changed its name to NG Energy International Corp. in November 2020. NG Energy International Corp. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
